'''Gimli''' was a [[Gnome]] in the early version of the [[legendarium]] in ''[[The Book of Lost Tales]]''. He was liberated from the thraldom of [[Tevildo]] along with [[Beren]]. His captivity had left him blind but with keen hearing.<ref>{{LT2|I}}, p. 29</ref>

==Etymology==
The [[Gnomish]] word ''gimli'' ("sense of hearing") is clearly related to this name.<ref>{{LT2|Appendix}}, entry "Gimli"</ref>

